<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portfolio | Visual Designer</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #000; color: #fff; cursor: crosshair; }
        .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: all 0.8s ease-out; }
        .reveal.active { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        .hover-scale img { transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); }
        .hover-scale:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .line-clamp-2 { display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 2; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="overflow-x-hidden">

    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 flex justify-between items-center px-8 py-6 mix-blend-difference">
        <div class="text-xl font-black tracking-tighter">STUDIO.DESIGN</div>
        <div class="space-x-8 text-sm font-medium hidden md:block">
            <a href="#work" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition">WORK</a>
            <a href="#about" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition">ABOUT</a>
            <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition">CONTACT</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-20">
        <h1 class="text-[12vw] leading-[0.9] font-black tracking-tighter uppercase mb-8">
            Visual<br><span class="text-gray-600">Storytelling</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed text-gray-400">
            专注文娱、IP与剧场空间的品牌视觉全案。通过设计连接观众心智与商业物理空间。
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="work" class="px-8 md:px-20 py-20 bg-white text-black rounded-t-[40px]">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase">Selected Work</h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hidden md:block">Scroll to explore</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
            
            <div class="md:col-span-8 reveal">
                <div class="hover-scale overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 rounded-xl mb-6 aspect-video">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1489599849927-2ee91cede3ba?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" alt="Theatre Project" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter">Orange Sky Golden Harvest</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">剧场品牌视觉重塑 / 3D 空间美陈</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs border border-black px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase font-bold">2024</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-4 self-center reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="hover-scale overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 rounded-xl mb-6 aspect-square">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626785774573-4b799315345d?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="IP Project" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase">Minions IP Campaign</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">国际IP衍生品设计与规范管控</p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-5 reveal">
                <div class="hover-scale overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 rounded-xl mb-6 aspect-[4/5]">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540575861501-7cf05a4b125a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Exhibition" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter italic">Foodaily Expo</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">千人级峰会全案视觉体系</p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-7 flex items-center px-10 reveal">
                <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light leading-tight italic">
                    "设计不仅是填充空间，<br>
                    而是创造<span class="font-black text-black not-italic underline decoration-4">有温度的连接</span>。"
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-40 px-8 bg-black text-white text-center">
        <h2 class="text-[10vw] font-black mb-10 tracking-tighter uppercase opacity-20">Contact</h2>
        <a href="mailto:your@email.com" class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold hover:text-gray-400 transition-all duration-300 underline underline-offset-8">
            GET IN TOUCH
        </a>
        <div class="mt-20 flex justify-center space-x-10 text-gray-600 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Behance</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">Instagram</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-white">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function reveal() {
            var reveals = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal");
            for (var i = 0; i < reveals.length; i++) {
                var windowHeight = window.innerHeight;
                var elementTop = reveals[i].getBoundingClientRect().top;
                var elementVisible = 150;
                if (elementTop < windowHeight - elementVisible) {
                    reveals[i].classList.add("active");
                }
            }
        }
        window.addEventListener("scroll", reveal);
        // 初始化一次
        reveal();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
